```plantuml
@startuml Neighbor-Army_help-with-covid

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Firebase Functions" as Backend
participant "Firebase Firestore" as Firestore
participant "Firebase Auth" as Auth
participant "Onfleet API" as Onfleet
participant "Sendgrid API" as Sendgrid
participant "Google Maps API" as GoogleMaps
participant "Twilio API" as Twilio

User -> Frontend: Access homepage (index.js)
Frontend -> Backend: Request homepage data
Backend -> Firestore: Retrieve data
Firestore --> Backend: Return data
Backend --> Frontend: Send homepage data
Frontend --> User: Display homepage

User -> Frontend: Signup to offer help (offer-help.js)
Frontend -> GoogleMaps: Address Autocomplete
GoogleMaps --> Frontend: Return address suggestions
Frontend -> Backend: Submit volunteer form
Backend -> Auth: Authenticate user
Auth --> Backend: Authentication success
Backend -> Onfleet: Create volunteer task
Onfleet --> Backend: Task created
Backend -> Sendgrid: Add to email list
Sendgrid --> Backend: Confirmation
Backend --> Frontend: Signup confirmation
Frontend --> User: Display confirmation

User -> Frontend: Request help instructions (request-help.js)
Frontend --> User: Display instructions

User -> Frontend: Login (auth.js)
Frontend -> Twilio: Verify phone/zipcode
Twilio --> Frontend: Verification success
Frontend -> Backend: Submit login
Backend -> Auth: Authenticate user
Auth --> Backend: Authentication success
Backend --> Frontend: Login success
Frontend --> User: Display user dashboard

@enduml
```